<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Gerar √çcone 512x512</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .icon-container {
            width: 512px;
            height: 512px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 100px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 128px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .icon-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 70% 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }
        
        .heart {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            filter: drop-shadow(4px 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3));
        }
        
        .text {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 40px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            z-index: 1;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        
        .instructions {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="icon-container">
        <div class="heart">üíù</div>
        <div class="text">AMMEA</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="instructions">
        <h3>Como salvar o √≠cone:</h3>
        <p>1. Clique direito no quadrado azul acima</p>
        <p>2. Selecione "Salvar imagem como..."</p>
        <p>3. Nomeie como <strong>icon-512.png</strong></p>
        <p>4. Salve na pasta <strong>assets/images/</strong></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>